### Get all products
GET http://localhost:5000/products HTTP/1.1

### Create product
POST http://localhost:5000/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name": "tea",
	"price": 1,
	"description": "a nice cup of tea",
	"sku": "a-a-a"
}

### Update product
PUT http://localhost:5000/products/1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"name": "hot chocolate milk",
	"Description": "a warm cup of chocolate milk"
}